title: Looking for duo partner.
body: Looking for a duo partner, nothing serious, just have some fun and play the game. Happy to play normals or ranked, doesn't matter what role you like, feel free to send me a tell! IGN: Fabien

replies.body:
Hey! I just made a post in the link below, but if you're interested in just some casual games, i can support (since it looks like you adc) c:
